# PawBon Project Rules / PawBon 项目规则

## Tech Stack / 技术栈
- Backend: Supabase Edge Functions (Deno/TypeScript)
- Frontend: LIFF (vanilla HTML/JS), LINE LIFF SDK
- Database: Supabase PostgreSQL
- Platform: LINE Messaging API

## Coding Conventions / 编码规范
- Edge Functions: TypeScript (Deno runtime)
- LIFF pages: vanilla JS (no framework / 无框架)
- Variables/functions: English camelCase / 变量和函数名用英文驼峰
- DB columns: snake_case / 数据库字段用下划线命名
- Timezone: JST (Asia/Tokyo) / 时区：日本标准时间
